Swipe Modes:

Left
Right
Both
None
Swipe Actions:

Reveal - Swipe to reveal a view behind the list item
Dismiss - Swipe to remove a list item from the list
Choice - Swipe with a rubber band-like behavior that toggles the selected state of the list item.
